1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,610 --> 00:01:41,039
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,750 --> 00:01:43,950
[Episode 32]

4
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:47,229
Send Heitou's confession

5
00:01:47,550 --> 00:01:48,830
to Hanzhou and Shazhou immediately

6
00:01:48,830 --> 00:01:49,750
and ask for their cooperative investigation.

7
00:01:49,750 --> 00:01:50,190
Yes.

8
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,020
Go to the place Heitou mentioned

9
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:54,110
to search for the goods.

10
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:54,509
Yes.

11
00:01:55,270 --> 00:01:56,030
Sheriff Lu.

12
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:02,590
I didn't expect

13
00:02:03,270 --> 00:02:04,510
that you

14
00:02:04,770 --> 00:02:06,200
accidentally caught

15
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:08,070
such a heinous criminal.

16
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,590
Congratulations.

17
00:02:10,590 --> 00:02:12,630
This is a great achievement.

18
00:02:15,230 --> 00:02:16,430
I haven't even figured out

19
00:02:16,430 --> 00:02:17,960
the cause of Li Yun's death.

20
00:02:18,230 --> 00:02:20,230
What's there to congratulate me on?

21
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:26,660
Just now, in front of Fed,

22
00:02:26,829 --> 00:02:28,140
I already admitted

23
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:30,840
I am an incompetent person.

24
00:02:32,350 --> 00:02:33,790
If you're still angry,

25
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:35,680
tonight,

26
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,380
in front of Xijun, Yingtao,

27
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:38,060
and Fed,

28
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:39,920
I will shout three more times

29
00:02:40,030 --> 00:02:42,350
that Su Wuming is an incompetent person.

30
00:02:43,070 --> 00:02:44,070
What do you think?

31
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:49,120
Don't think I'm trying to get back at you.

32
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,340
I'm not that petty.

33
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,520
It's just that...

34
00:02:52,990 --> 00:02:54,520
this case is truly bizarre.

35
00:02:54,550 --> 00:02:55,190
Indeed.

36
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:58,120
There are too many suspects.

37
00:02:58,970 --> 00:03:00,150
But it doesn't matter.

38
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,600
As long as we find them

39
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,520
one by one,

40
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:05,290
I believe we can definitely solve this case.

41
00:03:06,550 --> 00:03:07,150
Su Wuming.

42
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,080
Lu Lingfeng.

43
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,850
You finished drawing?

44
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:15,550
So soon?

45
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,710
They are just rough sketches.

46
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:22,030
I hope they can be helpful.

47
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:22,760
They will be.

48
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:24,180
When Ms. Yin saw them,

49
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,520
she said the portraits are so vivid.

50
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,320
She thought Xijun was a goddess.

51
00:03:27,990 --> 00:03:29,270
Actually, I'm thinking

52
00:03:29,270 --> 00:03:30,550
if more constables

53
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:32,150
in prefectures and counties

54
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,510
can have a painter to work with them,

55
00:03:33,510 --> 00:03:34,550
that would be great.

56
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:36,750
Are you making a suggestion to the court

57
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,010
or praising yourself?

58
00:03:38,990 --> 00:03:39,990
Both, I guess.

59
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,910
The portrait I drew was approved by the person depicted.

60
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:45,300
Can I... be proud of myself?

61
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:47,400
Of course you should be proud.

62
00:03:48,070 --> 00:03:48,710
I think

63
00:03:49,390 --> 00:03:50,710
your suggestion

64
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:51,820
is very good.

65
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,910
Someday in the future,

66
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,990
it might really become reality.

67
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:58,090
Then we should ask more people

68
00:03:58,829 --> 00:04:00,720
to enjoy the works

69
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,680
of the future best painter of Tang.

70
00:04:07,830 --> 00:04:08,360
This guy.

71
00:04:09,990 --> 00:04:11,150
I think I saw him

72
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:12,650
on the street two days ago.

73
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:14,030
How certain are you?

74
00:04:14,070 --> 00:04:15,630
I can't be completely certain.

75
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,990
Paste this portrait

76
00:04:17,180 --> 00:04:18,720
on the wall at the street corner now.

77
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,870
If the person in the portrait is still in Yunding,

78
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,230
don't let him leave the county.

79
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:22,630
Yes.

80
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:28,290
I've seen this person.

81
00:04:28,470 --> 00:04:29,230
That day...

82
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:32,550
They look alike.

83
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:34,290
They look very much alike.

84
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:36,040
At first, I didn't pay attention.

85
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,170
Later, I noticed...

86
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,000
At that time, I thought

87
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,780
rich men indeed know how to have fun.

88
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:42,880
They came outside

89
00:04:42,909 --> 00:04:43,940
instead of enjoying dances

90
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:44,990
in brothels.

91
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:46,140
And that woman

92
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:47,190
just let these two men

93
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,390
look at her from afar.

94
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:50,030
I wonder how much money she asked them for.

95
00:04:50,030 --> 00:04:51,090
Have you seen this kind of scene before

96
00:04:51,090 --> 00:04:52,830
on the street of Yunding?

97
00:04:53,470 --> 00:04:53,950
No.

98
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,350
It was the first time.

99
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:56,380
What about you guys?

100
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:57,120
-No.
-No.

101
00:04:57,150 --> 00:04:59,300
When did this happen?

102
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:00,840
Not long ago.

103
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,370
Three days ago?

104
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:03,470
No.

105
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,270
The day before yesterday.

106
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,190
Two days ago?

107
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:22,800
Mudan.

108
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,030
You know her?

109
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:24,560
Yes.

110
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:26,370
It really is Mudan.

111
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,150
The portrait is so vivid.

112
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:28,990
It's just that...

113
00:05:28,990 --> 00:05:31,310
the girl in the portrait is more beautiful than she really is.

114
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,710
Mudan is very beautiful.

115
00:05:33,030 --> 00:05:35,590
The portrait doesn't capture how coquettish she is in real life.

116
00:05:35,590 --> 00:05:36,390
Stop arguing.

117
00:05:36,790 --> 00:05:37,830
Which of you is close to her?

118
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:38,830
Go bring her here.

119
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,750
You thief, villain,

120
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:49,590
murderer!

121
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:53,100
[Mudan]

122
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:51,680
You lied to me by saying

123
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:53,720
you were a descendant of a noble family

124
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:55,750
and became a kiln worker after coming down in the world.

125
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:56,610
I didn't expect

126
00:05:56,710 --> 00:05:58,440
that you killed so many people!

127
00:05:58,790 --> 00:06:00,360
What bad luck!

128
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,190
Stop!

129
00:06:07,230 --> 00:06:08,830
I asked you to bring her here.

130
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,870
Why didn't you keep your mouth shut?

131
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:12,870
Don't blame him.

132
00:06:13,190 --> 00:06:14,650
We're old acquaintances.

133
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:16,420
Of course he'd tell me what's going on.

134
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,350
Besides,

135
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,400
if he didn't say it clearly,

136
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:21,140
I wouldn't have come here.

137
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,310
It's my fault.

138
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:24,410
I was blinded by him.

139
00:06:24,670 --> 00:06:25,600
He looks strong.

140
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:27,330
I thought he was an honest man.

141
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:28,210
I didn't expect

142
00:06:28,710 --> 00:06:30,640
that he would kill and rob someone!

143
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:35,030
It really scares me.

144
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:40,980
Sheriff Lu,

145
00:06:41,030 --> 00:06:41,830
we found these

146
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,950
in the stove

147
00:06:42,970 --> 00:06:44,770
in the house where Heitou lives.

148
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:53,420
You're this wealthy?

149
00:06:54,820 --> 00:06:56,820
Then why did you use my money?

150
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:58,990
You heartless bastard!

151
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:04,320
Except this silver ingot,

152
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,690
the rest of these

153
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:08,230
were obtained by killing and robbing others.

154
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:10,230
If you use them, won't you be scared?

155
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,330
Luckily, I've never spent a penny of his.

156
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:15,240
Mudan,

157
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,670
let me ask you.

158
00:07:17,110 --> 00:07:18,510
When did he arrive

159
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,750
at Biluo Inn yesterday?

160
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:20,680
He's a drunkard.

161
00:07:20,980 --> 00:07:22,860
He drank until midnight every day.

162
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:24,380
I think...

163
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:26,480
he arrived at my place at 11:00 p.m.

164
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:28,860
Right?

165
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:30,110
Yes.

166
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:30,710
Look.

167
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:32,270
What I said is true.

168
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:32,840
Shut up!

169
00:07:35,909 --> 00:07:37,640
What time did he leave your room

170
00:07:37,670 --> 00:07:38,590
in the morning?

171
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,430
When he left...

172
00:07:44,990 --> 00:07:47,110
I think... it was just after dawn.

173
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,330
Before that,

174
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:50,830
had Heitou ever left your room?

175
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:52,200
Absolutely not!

176
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:53,830
If he left halfway,

177
00:07:54,909 --> 00:07:56,790
what good is my charm?

178
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:06,800
What Mudan said

179
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:08,160
matches

180
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:09,730
Heitou's confession.

181
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:13,920
Li Yun died sometime between 9 p.m. and 11 p.m.

182
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,410
The time doesn't match up.

183
00:08:16,710 --> 00:08:17,350
Put Heitou

184
00:08:17,670 --> 00:08:18,560
in Yunding Prison!

185
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,140
-Yes!
-Yes!

186
00:08:19,140 --> 00:08:19,750
Wait.

187
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,760
I have something to say.

188
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:26,150
Be honest.

189
00:08:33,950 --> 00:08:34,470
Mudan,

190
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:36,130
I said I will marry you.

191
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:38,820
I meant it.

192
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:06,740
[Yunding County Office]

193
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:05,830
Sheriff Lu, you're walking me out.

194
00:09:05,830 --> 00:09:06,910
No need for this.

195
00:09:07,950 --> 00:09:09,190
Madam.

196
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,850
Who are you calling Madam?

197
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:13,520
I'm a young lady.

198
00:09:16,070 --> 00:09:17,030
Miss Mudan,

199
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,610
you are unmarried,

200
00:09:19,070 --> 00:09:19,470
but...

201
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:20,550
But what?

202
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,430
As long as it's not something

203
00:09:22,430 --> 00:09:23,960
forbidden by the Tang Code,

204
00:09:24,190 --> 00:09:25,110
I can do it.

205
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,610
I didn't say you violated the law.

206
00:09:27,830 --> 00:09:28,590
But you can't continue

207
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:29,520
to muddle along.

208
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:30,930
It's too dangerous

209
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,230
to associate with someone like Heitou.

210
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:35,290
Moreover, you are an appealing girl.

211
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:37,160
You deserve a decent life

212
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:38,480
and a bright future.

213
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:40,310
Live up to your name.

214
00:09:41,430 --> 00:09:41,830
You...

215
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:42,970
I...

216
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:45,470
You said I'm an appealing girl?

217
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:50,970
How come I don't feel that way myself?

218
00:09:52,990 --> 00:09:54,510
I'm sorry, Sheriff Lu.

219
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:57,270
I didn't speak properly just now.

220
00:09:58,190 --> 00:09:59,390
Sheriff Lu,

221
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:01,430
I'm very grateful

222
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:03,210
for your pearls of wisdom.

223
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,790
I will keep that in mind.

224
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:06,390
Do you have a proper livelihood?

225
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:06,830
Yes.

226
00:10:07,070 --> 00:10:07,950
I run a shop.

227
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:09,040
That's good.

228
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:11,170
I wish your business prosperity.

229
00:10:11,310 --> 00:10:12,190
I believe in you.

230
00:10:12,190 --> 00:10:13,030
In the future,

231
00:10:13,310 --> 00:10:15,440
you will find someone perfect for you.

232
00:10:16,830 --> 00:10:17,960
Sheriff, thank you.

233
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:20,430
Now,

234
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,450
we are acquaintances, right?

235
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:25,110
If I see you when I drink at the night market in the future,

236
00:10:25,110 --> 00:10:26,070
I will make a toast to you

237
00:10:26,070 --> 00:10:27,400
with three cups of wine.

238
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,620
Sheriff Lu, when you investigate a case,

239
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:40,270
you don't just focus on the case itself.

240
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:43,230
You do whatever you can to cure and save people.

241
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:46,110
I really admire you.

242
00:10:46,990 --> 00:10:48,150
Stop flattering me.

243
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:49,870
I still don't know

244
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:52,350
what to do next.

245
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:00,460
I know I was wrong.

246
00:11:00,830 --> 00:11:02,350
I really shouldn't have laughed.

247
00:11:02,350 --> 00:11:04,270
Yingtao and I are going back to cook now

248
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:05,200
as a punishment.

249
00:11:05,310 --> 00:11:06,510
You laughed in the court.

250
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:08,310
Indeed, you should be punished.

251
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,070
But...

252
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,550
you finished drawing the portraits.

253
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:12,670
That can be counted as a contribution.

254
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,750
Your fault can be offset by your contribution.

255
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:15,080
No need to cook tonight.

256
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:17,270
Let's go eat at the night market.

257
00:11:17,430 --> 00:11:17,990
My treat.

258
00:11:18,470 --> 00:11:19,140
Great.

259
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:22,470
I just received my monthly salary today.

260
00:11:22,470 --> 00:11:23,560
Ask Fed

261
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:25,350
to have a hearty meal with us.

262
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,620
You guys decide

263
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,800
what we eat tonight.

264
00:11:31,950 --> 00:11:32,830
Girls,

265
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:34,880
this is a rare opportunity.

266
00:11:35,050 --> 00:11:36,650
So take full advantage of it.

267
00:11:37,110 --> 00:11:38,080
We should go to a restaurant

268
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,070
with the most delicious food

269
00:11:39,070 --> 00:11:40,310
to put him to a lot of expense.

270
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:41,830
It doesn't matter if the food is delicious or not.

271
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:43,390
The point is we should order something expensive.

272
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:44,190
That's right.

273
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:46,920
Who asked him to always glare at us to scare us?

274
00:11:51,350 --> 00:11:52,710
Hunting the suspect.

275
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,510
They even put a bounty on him.

276
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:06,250
[Li Men]

277
00:12:07,270 --> 00:12:07,870
Li Men?

278
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:09,460
I don't know him.

279
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:10,910
Who is he?

280
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:12,150
Stop right there!

281
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:12,870
I have no idea.

282
00:12:12,870 --> 00:12:13,380
Bounty?

283
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:39,050
Your qinggong is impressive.

284
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,620
I don't know how to use qinggong at all.

285
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:41,790
If you don't know how to use qinggong,

286
00:12:41,790 --> 00:12:43,800
why are you so skilled at climbing over walls?

287
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:44,930
Climb over the wall.

288
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:48,750
Climb over the wall.

289
00:12:55,590 --> 00:12:56,150
Get out.

290
00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:04,490
Go back.

291
00:13:07,050 --> 00:13:07,690
Get out.

292
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:08,590
Go back.

293
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:09,250
Get out.

294
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:14,830
Speak!

295
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:20,110
I am from Hanzhou.

296
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,770
I no longer have

297
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:24,070
a means of making a living in my hometown.

298
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:25,930
So I want to try my luck in Shazhou.

299
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:28,460
I arrived in Yunding early in the morning the day before yesterday.

300
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:30,120
I didn't have much money left.

301
00:13:30,590 --> 00:13:32,870
I was worried I would starve to death on my way west.

302
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:35,030
So I thought of my cousin, Li Yun.

303
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:37,190
So you wrote him a letter.

304
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:39,070
Letter?

305
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,480
What letter?

306
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,470
You didn't write a letter to Li Yun

307
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:48,240
to tell him you came to Yunding?

308
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:51,790
What's the point of writing a letter to him?

309
00:13:52,430 --> 00:13:54,590
A few years ago, when I passed through Yunding,

310
00:13:54,590 --> 00:13:55,990
I stopped by his house.

311
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:58,570
But he didn't let me stay at his place.

312
00:13:58,830 --> 00:13:59,600
I had to

313
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,870
stay in an inn.

314
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:02,590
When he came to see me,

315
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:04,590
he only brought two pepper buns.

316
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:07,010
Why would I write him a letter?

317
00:14:09,090 --> 00:14:10,870
I just wanted to go

318
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,650
to his fabric shop at night.

319
00:14:13,230 --> 00:14:14,830
You wanted to steal from him?

320
00:14:14,950 --> 00:14:16,080
I did think about it.

321
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:18,590
But before I went there,

322
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:20,210
he came to Biluo Inn.

323
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:24,320
Cousin?

324
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,860
Li Men?

325
00:14:28,430 --> 00:14:30,830
You didn't write a letter to Li Yun.

326
00:14:30,850 --> 00:14:31,540
So

327
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:33,900
when you saw him in Biluo Inn,

328
00:14:34,310 --> 00:14:35,710
you were quite surprised.

329
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:36,310
Yes.

330
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,910
I even asked him,

331
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:38,730
"How did you know

332
00:14:38,730 --> 00:14:39,630
I live here?"

333
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:41,900
I'm very close to the soldiers at the city gate.

334
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:42,770
They told me

335
00:14:42,950 --> 00:14:44,080
you came to Yunding.

336
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:46,220
But how would the soldiers at the city gate

337
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:47,410
know who I am?

338
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:49,470
When we were drinking, I told them

339
00:14:49,470 --> 00:14:50,590
I have a cousin.

340
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:54,950
So you care so much

341
00:14:54,950 --> 00:14:55,950
about me.

342
00:14:56,310 --> 00:14:57,310
I misunderstood.

343
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:59,510
Your room is dark and damp.

344
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:01,230
The smell is really unpleasant.

345
00:15:01,230 --> 00:15:02,090
I'm going back.

346
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:02,990
Cousin.

347
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:04,670
You didn't come all the way

348
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:05,990
to Shangxian Lane

349
00:15:06,310 --> 00:15:08,280
just to see me, right?

350
00:15:08,310 --> 00:15:08,860
I did.

351
00:15:09,230 --> 00:15:10,430
I already saw you.

352
00:15:11,190 --> 00:15:11,920
I'm leaving.

353
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,070
Well...

354
00:15:13,350 --> 00:15:14,470
No need to walk me out.

355
00:15:14,470 --> 00:15:15,750
Don't leave this room.

356
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:18,590
Cousin.

357
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,030
To be honest with you,

358
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:22,750
I said I was just passing through Yunding.

359
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:26,050
But the truth is I have nowhere else to go.

360
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,550
Could you please

361
00:15:27,990 --> 00:15:28,750
help me?

362
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:31,270
I asked him to lend me some money.

363
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:33,230
But he said he was obsessed with cockfighting.

364
00:15:33,230 --> 00:15:36,360
He said he lost a lot of money and wouldn't lend me a penny.

365
00:15:37,470 --> 00:15:38,870
After he left, I thought

366
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:41,280
he definitely didn't come to see me.

367
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:43,730
At that time, I heard

368
00:15:43,730 --> 00:15:45,030
footsteps going upstairs.

369
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,830
When I checked in, I already knew

370
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:48,710
men and women in this county would often

371
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:50,910
go to this kind of family inn for trysts.

372
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:52,790
So I wanted to find out

373
00:15:52,930 --> 00:15:53,930
who he went to meet

374
00:15:54,070 --> 00:15:54,990
and then go to his house

375
00:15:54,990 --> 00:15:56,110
to tell his wife.

376
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:11,950
Honey.

377
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:15,950
You followed me here.

378
00:16:18,110 --> 00:16:20,840
You came here to have a tryst with a strange woman.

379
00:16:20,870 --> 00:16:22,110
I'm going to tell Shen Ping.

380
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:22,600
Don't.

381
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:27,570
You want me to keep it a secret for you?

382
00:16:28,710 --> 00:16:30,240
Give me five silver ingots.

383
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,950
I want to go to Shazhou to explore a cave.

384
00:16:31,950 --> 00:16:33,670
After that, I can definitely support myself

385
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:35,390
and I'll never come back to you again.

386
00:16:35,390 --> 00:16:36,710
Five silver ingots?

387
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:37,830
Are you crazy?

388
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:39,850
What's wrong with that?

389
00:16:39,850 --> 00:16:41,110
Your father-in-law left you

390
00:16:41,110 --> 00:16:42,950
the biggest fabric shop in Yunding.

391
00:16:42,950 --> 00:16:44,230
Just five silver ingots.

392
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:44,830
Is it a lot?

393
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:50,160
You won't give it to me, right?

394
00:16:50,740 --> 00:16:51,510
If you won't,

395
00:16:52,310 --> 00:16:54,510
I'll make you lose all your reputation!

396
00:16:54,550 --> 00:16:55,390
How dare you!

397
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:57,980
How dare you blackmail me!

398
00:16:57,980 --> 00:16:59,440
How dare you blackmail me!

399
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:01,990
How dare you!

400
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,589
You bastard.

401
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:10,140
You're a good-for-nothing who can't even afford a meal.

402
00:17:10,140 --> 00:17:11,170
How dare you blackmail me!

403
00:17:11,170 --> 00:17:12,430
I am blackmailing you!

404
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:13,859
If you don't give me the money today,

405
00:17:13,859 --> 00:17:14,750
I'll make sure everyone in this county

406
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:15,910
knows about this!

407
00:17:52,990 --> 00:17:53,550
Chu Bin!

408
00:17:54,260 --> 00:17:54,970
A ghost!

409
00:18:03,390 --> 00:18:04,190
What's wrong?

410
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:05,550
You look so scared.

411
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:07,670
Did you see a ghost?

412
00:18:12,190 --> 00:18:13,110
Chu Bin?

413
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:13,910
Yes.

414
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,410
She died ten years ago.

415
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:17,370
When she was alive,

416
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:18,830
was she very close to you?

417
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,630
She was Li Yun's former wife.

418
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:22,190
No.

419
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:24,190
They never had a formal wedding ceremony.

420
00:18:24,190 --> 00:18:25,110
But when Chu Bin was alive,

421
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,510
she loved wearing a veil.

422
00:18:26,970 --> 00:18:28,030
What I saw last night

423
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:29,250
really is a female ghost.

424
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:30,640
She looked exactly the same

425
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:32,240
as Chu Bin when she was alive.

426
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:35,910
Li Men,

427
00:18:36,790 --> 00:18:37,990
get up.

428
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:39,110
Come.

429
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:40,500
Get up.

430
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:42,520
My legs are numb.

431
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:47,270
Tell us everything

432
00:18:47,430 --> 00:18:50,030
you know.

433
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:52,950
Thank you.

434
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:55,630
At that time,

435
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:57,790
my parents were still alive.

436
00:18:57,790 --> 00:18:58,850
My family was rich.

437
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:01,500
So I often came to Yunding to have fun.

438
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:08,720
Cousin?

439
00:19:10,390 --> 00:19:11,020
Li Men?

440
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:15,470
Cousin,

441
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:17,110
this is...

442
00:19:18,110 --> 00:19:19,270
Are you married?

443
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:21,910
Why didn't you write a letter to my father to tell us about it?

444
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:22,970
Her name is Chu Bin.

445
00:19:23,260 --> 00:19:25,350
She came to Yunding from Dongdu with me.

446
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:27,070
Marriage is significant

447
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:29,270
and requires careful consideration.

448
00:19:29,270 --> 00:19:30,400
If we really plan to get married,

449
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:32,060
I will write a letter to your father

450
00:19:32,060 --> 00:19:32,870
and invite him

451
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:35,110
to officiate at our wedding in Yunding.

452
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,390
That's more like it.

453
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:39,230
Chu Bin.

454
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:41,810
My future sister-in-law.

455
00:19:42,430 --> 00:19:43,300
I'm Li Men.

456
00:19:43,670 --> 00:19:44,750
Greetings.

457
00:19:45,430 --> 00:19:46,760
Nice to meet you, Mr. Li.

458
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:48,670
Come, Cousin.

459
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:51,050
Chu Bin is such a good cook.

460
00:19:51,710 --> 00:19:53,070
You're lucky.

461
00:19:54,390 --> 00:19:55,520
Apart from cooking,

462
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:56,780
she knows how to write too.

463
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:57,310
Really?

464
00:19:57,830 --> 00:19:58,270
Come.

465
00:20:02,750 --> 00:20:04,230
By copying books for the bookstore,

466
00:20:04,230 --> 00:20:06,290
she can make a lot of money each month.

467
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:13,650
Have a seat, Mr. Li.

468
00:20:14,190 --> 00:20:16,190
You finally have a chance to meet each other.

469
00:20:16,190 --> 00:20:18,190
You should drink and chat all night.

470
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:19,920
I won't disturb you.

471
00:20:25,570 --> 00:20:27,970
She is such a beautiful and virtuous woman.

472
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:28,710
Cousin,

473
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:30,640
you're really something.

474
00:20:32,150 --> 00:20:33,010
One year later,

475
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,640
namely ten years ago,

476
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:37,640
I remember it was also this season.

477
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:39,980
That day was the Cold Food Festival.

478
00:20:41,150 --> 00:20:42,480
I came to Yunding again.

479
00:20:48,270 --> 00:20:48,820
Cousin.

480
00:20:50,790 --> 00:20:52,430
Cousin, you're here.

481
00:20:54,190 --> 00:20:55,390
Whose coffin is this?

482
00:20:58,750 --> 00:20:59,470
Chu Bin's.

483
00:21:00,910 --> 00:21:01,630
Do you know

484
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:03,430
how Chu Bin died?

485
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,050
Li Yun said she

486
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:06,810
died of a sudden acute illness.

487
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:08,350
But Chu Bin was so young.

488
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:10,220
What acute illness could she have?

489
00:21:10,220 --> 00:21:11,240
I think she died

490
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:11,750
because Li Yun

491
00:21:11,750 --> 00:21:12,750
had a new lover.

492
00:21:13,230 --> 00:21:14,290
What a pity. Chu Bin

493
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:16,350
was a graceful and virtuous lady.

494
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,610
She was also talented.

495
00:21:18,070 --> 00:21:20,470
She was born in Dongdu, but died in Yunding.

496
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:27,350
Right,

497
00:21:28,340 --> 00:21:29,540
why did you arrest me?

498
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:31,240
What crime did I commit?

499
00:21:34,430 --> 00:21:36,060
If you're innocent, why were you running?

500
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:38,120
You pasted my portrait on the street.

501
00:21:38,140 --> 00:21:38,510
I...

502
00:21:39,230 --> 00:21:40,230
I felt nervous.

503
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:42,870
You felt nervous because you killed Li Yun!

504
00:21:42,870 --> 00:21:43,270
You...

505
00:21:46,670 --> 00:21:47,150
What?

506
00:21:48,070 --> 00:21:49,270
Li Yun is dead?

507
00:21:51,210 --> 00:21:52,610
It must be Chu Bin's ghost

508
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:53,690
that took his life.

509
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:56,890
This further proves my speculation.

510
00:21:57,140 --> 00:21:59,200
Then tell us about your speculation.

511
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,170
Your Honor,

512
00:22:00,230 --> 00:22:01,270
ten years ago, I already felt

513
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,950
Chu Bin's death was very suspicious.

514
00:22:02,950 --> 00:22:03,910
Now that I think about it,

515
00:22:03,910 --> 00:22:04,910
I think Li Yun

516
00:22:04,910 --> 00:22:06,430
killed Chu Bin

517
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:08,110
in order to marry Shen Ping successfully.

518
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:09,790
You can't make a wild guess

519
00:22:09,990 --> 00:22:11,950
at this kind of thing.

520
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:13,870
It's not a wild guess.

521
00:22:14,110 --> 00:22:15,590
After they returned to Yunding,

522
00:22:15,590 --> 00:22:17,000
Li Yun met Shen Ping

523
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:18,150
when he was learning the craft of tailoring.

524
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:19,830
Then he grew tired of Chu Bin and fell in love with Shen Ping.

525
00:22:19,830 --> 00:22:20,670
Chu Bin wrote me a letter

526
00:22:20,670 --> 00:22:21,870
to tell me about this.

527
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,910
I could feel how heartbroken she was from each word she wrote.

528
00:22:23,910 --> 00:22:25,250
It's been ten years since this happened.

529
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:27,050
But the letter is still in my bag.

530
00:22:27,390 --> 00:22:28,250
Where is my bag?

531
00:22:45,990 --> 00:22:48,230
Mr. Li Men,

532
00:22:49,390 --> 00:22:50,710
I apologize

533
00:22:50,710 --> 00:22:52,030
for writing a letter to you suddenly.

534
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:53,390
Let me explain.

535
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:56,630
Li Yun is about to let me down.

536
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:59,720
I hope you have time

537
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:01,070
to hear my story now.

538
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:04,590
Recently, Li Yun has been learning the craft of tailoring in a fabric shop.

539
00:23:04,590 --> 00:23:07,340
He met the shop owner's daughter, Shen Ping.

540
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:09,800
So he has become more distant from me.

541
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,960
But I also know

542
00:23:12,070 --> 00:23:13,340
we need money

543
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:14,630
to live our lives.

544
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:17,100
It'll be difficult if we don't have a skill

545
00:23:17,790 --> 00:23:18,850
to making a living.

546
00:23:19,190 --> 00:23:21,480
So I can't stop him from learning the craft.

547
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,670
If I don't stop him,

548
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:25,630
Li Yun and Shen Ping will become a couple.

549
00:23:25,990 --> 00:23:28,670
Then I'll be alone.

550
00:23:29,530 --> 00:23:31,340
It'll be a challenge to me too.

551
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:34,290
You know I love Li Yun very much.

552
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:35,980
I don't want to let him go.

553
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:37,810
Could you please help me

554
00:23:37,910 --> 00:23:40,550
persuade Li Yun to change his mind?

555
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:42,410
Thank you. Thank you again.

556
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:44,270
Chu Bin.

557
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:51,130
This letter does look like something from ten years ago.

