00:24:11,030 --> 00:24:12,630
Li Men doesn't know martial arts.

563
00:24:12,630 --> 00:24:13,860
I've seen him

564
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:15,200
climb over walls myself.

565
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,710
If he wants to climb down from here,

566
00:24:16,710 --> 00:24:17,590
to him,

567
00:24:17,950 --> 00:24:19,410
it wouldn't be difficult.

568
00:24:20,060 --> 00:24:21,260
If he had to climb down

569
00:24:21,820 --> 00:24:22,820
from this height,

570
00:24:23,350 --> 00:24:25,150
unless he encountered a ghost

