00:24:35,390 --> 00:24:36,990
who climbed down from above?

576
00:24:37,150 --> 00:24:37,880
Yes, indeed.

577
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,550
He looked flustered,

578
00:24:39,710 --> 00:24:41,390
as if he had just seen a ghost.

579
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:43,220
Ms. Yin sells joss paper

580
00:24:43,470 --> 00:24:45,030
and runs this private inn.

581
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,710
All the wandering ghosts and spirits

582
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:48,510
should be fighting to stay here.

583
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:49,960
Take a look.

584
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:51,550
Is it this the person?

585
00:25:02,350 --> 00:25:03,010
That's him.

586
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:05,270
Do you remember what time it was?

587
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:07,070
It was just getting dark.

588
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:07,600
As for me,

589
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:09,430
I don't set up my stall at night.

590
00:25:09,430 --> 00:25:11,750
I had just packed up and was heading back.

591
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:13,000
Around 7 to 9 p.m.?

592
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:13,440
Yes.

593
00:25:13,710 --> 00:25:15,700
It was at about 7 p.m..

594
00:25:17,230 --> 00:25:17,790
Alright.

595
00:25:18,190 --> 00:25:19,320
Thank you very much.

596
00:25:19,470 --> 00:25:21,330
I wish you a prosperous business.

597
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:29,880
When Li Men climbed down from above,

598
00:25:29,950 --> 00:25:31,550
it was at about 7 p.m..

599
00:25:32,270 --> 00:25:34,590
We also happened to run into a witness.

600
00:25:35,170 --> 00:25:37,720
But Li Yun died within 9 to 11 p.m..

601
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:40,250
The timing doesn't match.

602
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:42,580
Well, I wouldn't rule out the possibility

603
00:25:42,580 --> 00:25:44,910
that Li Men came back to commit the murder.

604
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:50,000
As Li Men was evasive with his words,

605
00:25:50,030 --> 00:25:52,340
it indeed raises more suspicion.

606
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:55,670
Let's go back and interrogate him further.

607
00:25:58,140 --> 00:25:58,630
Li Men.

608
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:00,950
After escaping from Biluo Inn,

609
00:26:01,150 --> 00:26:02,080
where did you go?

610
00:26:05,570 --> 00:26:06,390
I didn't go anywhere.

611
00:26:06,390 --> 00:26:06,920
Suo Long.

612
00:26:07,460 --> 00:26:08,120
Mr. Li

613
00:26:08,150 --> 00:26:09,590
doesn't want to confess the truth.

614
00:26:09,590 --> 00:26:11,270
According to the county government's rules,

615
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,270
what should we do?

616
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:13,410
Drag him out

617
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:15,350
and give him 20 lashes first.

618
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:17,030
No, no, no.

619
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:17,990
I'll tell you.

620
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:25,190
I went to Tianyi Fabric Shop.

621
00:26:25,550 --> 00:26:27,750
You've already caught Li Yun's weakness,

622
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,590
so you went to

623
00:26:28,890 --> 00:26:29,820
blackmail him?

624
00:26:35,060 --> 00:26:35,910
Dear customer,

625
00:26:35,910 --> 00:26:36,760
we are closed.

626
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:39,020
If you want to make clothes, please come back tomorrow.

627
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:40,430
Yes, young man.

628
00:26:40,630 --> 00:26:42,230
It's too dark to see clearly.

629
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:43,470
It would be no good

630
00:26:43,470 --> 00:26:44,260
if you make a mistake

631
00:26:44,260 --> 00:26:45,790
when choosing your fabric.

632
00:26:46,590 --> 00:26:48,030
With how poor I look,

633
00:26:48,190 --> 00:26:50,320
do I look like I can afford new clothes?

634
00:26:50,620 --> 00:26:51,880
I want to see Shen Ping.

635
00:26:54,670 --> 00:26:55,270
Mr. Li.

636
00:26:55,710 --> 00:26:57,500
Madam had just gone to bed.

637
00:26:58,350 --> 00:26:59,150
She's asleep?

638
00:26:59,990 --> 00:27:00,990
So early?

639
00:27:02,070 --> 00:27:02,990
It doesn't bother her

640
00:27:02,990 --> 00:27:04,270
that her husband is still out?

641
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,310
For the past year,

642
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:07,610
my madam's health has been very frail.

643
00:27:07,990 --> 00:27:10,070
Even eating a meal exhausts her.

644
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,350
But she won't be asleep for long.

645
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:14,280
She'll wake up in two hours at most.

646
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:17,550
But... I dare not wake her up now.

647
00:27:18,290 --> 00:27:19,490
If she gets startled,

648
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:20,670
it would be a sin.

649
00:27:22,230 --> 00:27:23,270
Two hours.

650
00:27:25,470 --> 00:27:26,800
Fine, I'll wait for her.

651
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:30,470
I am Li Yun's cousin.

652
00:27:30,990 --> 00:27:31,830
Aren't you guys going to

653
00:27:31,830 --> 00:27:33,830
prepare some food and drinks for me?

654
00:27:33,950 --> 00:27:36,210
Don't make me wait with an empty stomach.

655
00:27:36,210 --> 00:27:38,070
I ate and drank my fill and waited.

656
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:39,630
I waited until

657
00:27:40,070 --> 00:27:40,990
12 midnight.

658
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:45,820
It's really my cousin.

659
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:47,680
Sister-in-law.

660
00:27:47,830 --> 00:27:49,290
It's only been a few years.

661
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:50,910
How did you become so ill?

662
00:27:52,670 --> 00:27:53,790
After turning 30,

663
00:27:53,980 --> 00:27:55,910
I've been getting worse day by day.

664
00:27:56,270 --> 00:27:57,080
Brother,

665
00:27:57,110 --> 00:27:58,570
sorry to keep you waiting.

666
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:01,590
Didn't Li Yun went to find you?

667
00:28:02,010 --> 00:28:03,030
You two brothers

668
00:28:03,090 --> 00:28:04,420
didn't meet each other?

669
00:28:04,530 --> 00:28:05,480
Li Yun had no intention

670
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:06,610
to look for me at all.

671
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,040
It seems you guys had a fight.

672
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:15,360
No matter how much you argue or fight,

673
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,750
you're still family.

674
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:18,150
Don't hold grudges, okay?

675
00:28:18,150 --> 00:28:19,910
He really didn't come looking for me.

676
00:28:19,910 --> 00:28:21,440
There was a letter from you.

677
00:28:21,470 --> 00:28:23,580
Master only left after reading your letter.

678
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:24,470
If he hadn't looked for you,

679
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:25,790
then who was he looking for?

680
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,190
I never wrote any letter.

681
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:30,140
Was it my handwriting on the letter?

682
00:28:31,020 --> 00:28:32,110
I can't read.

683
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:36,610
Did you read the letter, sister-in-law?

684
00:28:36,610 --> 00:28:38,410
Your cousin didn't show it to me.

685
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:40,120
Well, there you have it.

686
00:28:41,190 --> 00:28:42,260
He has a guilty conscience.

687
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:44,260
Of course he wouldn't show it to you.

688
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:45,500
I did indeed

689
00:28:45,530 --> 00:28:47,660
run into him at the inn I was staying at.

690
00:28:47,670 --> 00:28:48,200
But he...

691
00:28:52,230 --> 00:28:55,290
Sister-in-law, please have your servant leave first.

692
00:28:59,870 --> 00:29:01,330
After all, he is my cousin.

693
00:29:02,110 --> 00:29:04,040
For the sake of my uncle's dignity,

694
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:04,920
I can't let him

695
00:29:04,950 --> 00:29:07,310
disgrace himself in front of the servants.

696
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:09,510
But my cousin-in-law Shen Ping, she...

697
00:29:11,870 --> 00:29:12,670
Brother.

698
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,870
It's not that I want to reprimand you.

699
00:29:14,870 --> 00:29:16,750
You and my husband bear the same surname.

700
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:18,480
How could you not be on his side?

701
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:20,470
What do you mean?

702
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:22,360
You shouldn't have said

703
00:29:22,390 --> 00:29:23,650
what you said just now.

704
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:26,920
You definitely shouldn't have said it in front of me.

705
00:29:31,710 --> 00:29:32,950
You're poor

706
00:29:33,590 --> 00:29:35,150
and you wanted my family to help you.

707
00:29:35,150 --> 00:29:36,740
Your cousin felt exasperated towards you.

708
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:37,670
He was mad at you,

709
00:29:38,150 --> 00:29:39,780
so he didn't give you any money.

710
00:29:39,780 --> 00:29:41,150
No, I...

711
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,410
It's also my fault.

712
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:43,410
When I went out,

713
00:29:43,830 --> 00:29:45,830
I only gave him a small silver ingot.

714
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:49,870
Wait here.

715
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:54,660
Take these two silver ingots

716
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:55,470
and leave.

717
00:29:56,550 --> 00:29:58,150
I considered you a relative.

718
00:29:58,190 --> 00:29:59,350
But you said such

719
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,750
awful things about my husband.

720
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:01,590
Don't ever

721
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:02,920
come to our house again.

722
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,570
Sister-in-law.

723
00:30:04,630 --> 00:30:04,950
I...

724
00:30:05,670 --> 00:30:06,190
Mr. Li.

725
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,560
It's time to leave.

726
00:30:11,410 --> 00:30:13,210
That was given to me by Shen Ping.

727
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:15,130
Whether I can turn the remaining of my life around,

728
00:30:15,130 --> 00:30:16,550
depends on these two silver ingots.

729
00:30:16,550 --> 00:30:17,170
You guys must not

730
00:30:17,170 --> 00:30:18,030
take them away.

731
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:21,140
Are you referring to

732
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:22,140
these two ingots?

733
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:23,590
Yes, yes.

734
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:26,070
Bring out the stolen goods from Heitou's place

735
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:27,000
for comparison.

736
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:43,690
[Tianyi Fabric Shop]

737
00:30:45,870 --> 00:30:46,920
These silver ingots

738
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:48,450
were left to me by my father.

739
00:30:49,410 --> 00:30:50,470
All of them aren't big.

740
00:30:50,470 --> 00:30:52,430
It's just for the fabric shop's convenience.

741
00:30:52,430 --> 00:30:53,960
Today at the county government,

742
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:55,220
why didn't you mention

743
00:30:55,350 --> 00:30:57,680
the matter of Li Men getting blackmailed?

744
00:30:57,770 --> 00:30:59,830
That's not exactly blackmail, is it?

745
00:31:00,390 --> 00:31:02,030
When you have such poor relatives,

746
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:04,290
it's inevitable to lose a bit of fortune.

747
00:31:04,490 --> 00:31:06,950
It's also a way to share my husband's burden.

748
00:31:07,270 --> 00:31:07,950
Besides,

749
00:31:08,670 --> 00:31:09,990
one mustn't air dirty laundry in public.

750
00:31:09,990 --> 00:31:11,350
Madam, you are virtuous,

751
00:31:11,350 --> 00:31:13,280
but perhaps a little too virtuous.

752
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:16,060
At what time did Li Men leave?

753
00:31:16,430 --> 00:31:17,290
Around 11 p.m..

754
00:31:17,390 --> 00:31:18,470
When I sent him out,

755
00:31:18,630 --> 00:31:20,160
I heard the night watchman.

756
00:31:25,930 --> 00:31:28,130
[County]

757
00:31:32,090 --> 00:31:33,620
The testimonies from Li Men

758
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:35,710
and the master and servant of Tianyi Fabric Shop

759
00:31:35,710 --> 00:31:36,910
indeed corroborate.

760
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,530
As you deduced,

761
00:31:38,650 --> 00:31:40,380
Li Yun died between 9 to 11 p.m..

762
00:31:40,430 --> 00:31:41,160
If so, Li Men

763
00:31:41,430 --> 00:31:43,470
didn't have time to commit the crime.

764
00:31:43,470 --> 00:31:44,310
Yes.

765
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:46,590
But I still need to detain Li Men

766
00:31:46,590 --> 00:31:47,710
at Yunding Prison

767
00:31:47,870 --> 00:31:49,470
until the truth is revealed.

768
00:31:52,190 --> 00:31:53,150
What for?

769
00:31:54,830 --> 00:31:55,490
Sheriff Lu.

770
00:32:02,060 --> 00:32:02,840
Li Men said

771
00:32:03,100 --> 00:32:04,870
he once hit Li Yun with a candlestick.

772
00:32:04,870 --> 00:32:06,500
It happened on the second floor,

773
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,030
but in the room on the second floor,

774
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:09,830
we couldn't find this said candlestick.

775
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:10,550
However, Xijun found it

776
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:12,150
in the room on the first floor

777
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,420
where Li Men lived.

778
00:32:14,430 --> 00:32:16,390
So, it's possible that

779
00:32:16,410 --> 00:32:17,870
after the murderer killed the victim,

780
00:32:17,870 --> 00:32:19,910
he rearranged the crime scene.

781
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:22,500
Sheriff Lu.

782
00:32:22,910 --> 00:32:24,790
You had investigated the murder scene

783
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:26,430
so thoroughly.

784
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:28,220
I am indeed impressed.

785
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:29,600
Alright,

786
00:32:30,270 --> 00:32:31,800
stop praising me like this.

787
00:32:32,830 --> 00:32:34,640
You aren't trying to ask me to give you

788
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:35,990
your monthly salary as soon as possible, are you?

789
00:32:35,990 --> 00:32:36,720
I, Su Wuming,

790
00:32:37,030 --> 00:32:38,450
has this exact intention.

791
00:32:38,450 --> 00:32:40,280
Then why don't you analyze this case at once?

792
00:32:40,280 --> 00:32:42,210
You think you get paid for nothing?

793
00:32:43,910 --> 00:32:44,590
Currently,

794
00:32:45,140 --> 00:32:46,960
there are two other suspects.

795
00:32:47,170 --> 00:32:49,970
One is that veiled woman,

796
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:50,930
and the other

797
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:52,590
is that ugly woman.

798
00:32:53,170 --> 00:32:53,950
Sheriff Lu!

799
00:32:56,430 --> 00:32:57,090
Sheriff Lu!

800
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:59,350
The veiled woman has been found.

801
00:32:59,350 --> 00:32:59,830
Where?

802
00:33:00,390 --> 00:33:01,230
Anyuan Inn.

803
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:04,970
[Anyuan Inn]

804
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:12,340
Mr. Xu.

805
00:33:12,670 --> 00:33:13,240
How is it?

806
00:33:13,550 --> 00:33:14,350
It's amazing.

807
00:33:14,540 --> 00:33:15,150
Amazing!

808
00:33:15,950 --> 00:33:18,150
She can really transform into my cousin.

809
00:33:18,150 --> 00:33:18,750
Moreover,

810
00:33:18,990 --> 00:33:20,650
it's exactly how my cousin looked

811
00:33:20,650 --> 00:33:21,910
when I was 16 years old.

812
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:24,680
After all these years, I finally get to see her again.

813
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:26,440
I can die without regrets now.

814
00:33:26,910 --> 00:33:29,110
Then Mr. Xu, you can now rekindle your old flames,

815
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:30,550
and renew your love affair.

816
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:31,350
Despicable!

817
00:33:31,870 --> 00:33:33,110
Back then, my cousin and I

818
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:34,790
were completely innocent.

819
00:33:35,070 --> 00:33:36,240
Then, you didn't spend these

820
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,470
few silver ingots in vain.

821
00:33:37,470 --> 00:33:39,350
Look at how petty you are.

822
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:40,100
So vulgar.

823
00:33:40,510 --> 00:33:41,840
How unbearably vulgar!

824
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:45,450
Gentlemen,

825
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:46,330
this way.

826
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:54,260
It's this room.

827
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:55,960
The person is inside.

828
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:58,310
She claims to be seeing a client.

829
00:34:03,110 --> 00:34:03,710
Who is it?

830
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:05,070
A client.

831
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,880
How could you be a client

832
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:09,290
when you didn't make an appointment?

833
00:34:14,270 --> 00:34:16,310
Yunding County's sheriff investigating a case.

834
00:34:16,310 --> 00:34:17,570
Open the door quickly.

835
00:34:34,860 --> 00:34:35,860
My name is Lin Bei.

836
00:34:36,290 --> 00:34:38,590
[Lin Bei]

837
00:34:36,750 --> 00:34:38,949
I live near Beimang Mountain in Dongdu.

838
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,560
I came to Yunding

839
00:34:41,230 --> 00:34:42,489
exactly one month ago.

840
00:34:43,110 --> 00:34:44,639
As for what I came here to do,

841
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,350
if you two

842
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:47,710
had encountered

843
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:49,190
Mr. Xu who just left,

844
00:34:49,989 --> 00:34:51,389
you should already know.

845
00:34:57,690 --> 00:35:00,190
That day, I went to the Biluo Inn.

846
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:02,510
I heard fighting sounds

847
00:35:02,510 --> 00:35:03,970
coming from another room.

848
00:35:04,230 --> 00:35:05,830
So I took a lamp to take a look.

849
00:35:06,310 --> 00:35:07,770
It turned out to be two men.

850
00:35:09,310 --> 00:35:10,770
One of them saw me and said,

851
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,030
"Chu Bin?

852
00:35:15,630 --> 00:35:16,430
A ghost!"

853
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,840
He seemed to have really saw a ghost.

854
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:21,390
He actually jumped out of the window and fled.

855
00:35:21,390 --> 00:35:22,650
As for the other guy...

856
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:32,550
Chu Bin.

857
00:35:34,130 --> 00:35:35,260
It's been ten years.

858
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:37,610
We've been separated by death.

859
00:35:38,950 --> 00:35:39,950
How have you been?

860
00:35:40,870 --> 00:35:42,730
I know Chu Bin is also from Dongdu.

861
00:35:42,990 --> 00:35:43,650
Otherwise,

862
00:35:43,830 --> 00:35:45,560
